item.title: How Entrepreneurs and CEOs Can Build Their Companies - Kurt Wilkin
item.description: Kurt Wilkin is a gifted connector—of dots, ideas, and people. For the past thirty years, he has advised high-growth companies, starting his career with Ernst & Young, and today in his roles as co-founder and visionary of HireBetter and managing partner of Bee Cave Capital. He is a serial entrepreneur with multiple successful exits and has helped hundreds of entrepreneurs and CEOs build their companies... Feed: https://app.kajabi.com/podcasts/2147485849/feed
